Classes we might use:

- Airport

- Person (abstract Parent)
	children:
	- pilot
	- coPilot
	- passengers
	- onBoardStaff (stewardess/etc.)
	- maintenanceStaff (maybe)
	- ground staff (maybe)

- Plane (abstract Parent)
	children:
	- B747 (Boeing 747 Model)
	- B777 (Boeing 777 Model)
	- A320 (Airbus A320 Model)

- Luggage (Parent) //not abstract because we could use luggage in general as additional weight or something
	- checkedLuggage
	- carryOnLuggage
